<title>Python Inline Scripts with uv</title>

<example>
uv run --no-project -q --script - < <(cat <<'EOF'
# /// script
# dependencies = [
#   "httpx" # Only PyPI packages - NOT stdlib modules like json, os, re
# ]
# requires-python = ">=3.12" # ALWAYS assume Python 3.12+, PEP 585
# ///

import httpx
print(httpx.get("https://api.github.com/zen").text)
EOF
)
</example>

